问题：
    1. 无法git clone  
	查看下  $env | grep -i proxy
		NO_PROXY=localhost,127.0.0.0/8,::1
		https_proxy=http://127.0.0.1:37152/
		HTTPS_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:37152/
		no_proxy=localhost,127.0.0.0/8,::1
	打开/home/keetsky/.gitconfig 文件,win7在C:\Users\tom目录下，添加如下
		[http]
        		proxy = ""
					
	最终我的.gitconfig为
		[user]
			name = keetsky
			email = keetsky@163.com
		[color]
			ui = true

		[http]
			proxy = ""

		[credential]
			helper = store
